<subSubSection pageId="28" pageNumber="43" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="28" pageNumber="43">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="28" pageNumber="43">Small (4.0-6.8 mm); vestiture of seta-like scales and setae; scape medium-sized (reaching eye when resting in scrobe); elytra with small, rounded tubercles.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
